title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 4 2022

description:
Biden visits crime-infested NYC. Former NYC Police Commissioner Bratton says it will be "historic struggle" to turn NYC crime around. NYC Democrat says Defund the Police is dead. Buck says, "It is not the insurrectionists of January 6th that are clubbing old ladies and throwing innocent people in front of trains. It is career criminals." Democrats don't care about securing our border. Shaq rejects vax mandates.
